 	<div class="modal-body">
        	<div class="container-fluid text-center">
			<h2>A Riverside Date</h2>
			<h4>How Love is metaphorically a Butterfly effect. <br>
The days seemed to be sinking in mire until the photograph flashed <br>
Your smile appeared like blushing Camellia-A Gift to a Man <br>
It felt like God has poured the happiness and heart got Love splashed, <br>
rekindled my hope like white Zinnia and lengthened my Life Span. <br>
When you spoke the soothing voice tuned my soul into music, <br>
Your lips were like a piano which strive to inspire and provided motivation.<br> 
Your presence which I felt was enough to create a magic,<br> 
My existence looked justified and my liveliness earned the passion.<br> 
Suddenly the aim which looked like a pale jaded mountain, now appeared vivid <br>
and whenever you sat beside me it seemed as if whole world is nearby.<br> 
I failed many times but you always prevented me from getting livid,<br>
and when I dreamt , you filled colors and never let my hopes to die.<br> 
One day we had a fight and I had to leave though I never wanted,<br> 
but when you left, my luck worsened and I met an accident.<br> 
Next day when I woke to sleep your voice once again enchanted,<br> 
and You took care like a mother and ordered as a president.<br> 
Your love healed every wounds and rejoiced the hope,<br> 
Your affection melted the frozen sea and illuminated the springs'<br> 
I once again regained the path and changed my horoscope<br> 
All the perturbing mystery was now solved which gave wings.<br>
 The love brought all the turnaround and made successful<br> 
A long time from now will be really soon,<br> 
You're my wife and life which made it less stressful,<br> 
who came as Scarlet Peonies but later became a divine boon.<br> 
Love is a perfect example of 'The Butterfly Effect' ,<br> 
where a small change initially can bring drastic changes.<br> 
Like an adorable smile gained me the love and respect,<br> 
which crossed all the limits and surpassed all the ranges.<br> 
My stomach fluttered as if it is the wings of Butterfly,<br>
My heart thumped as if it has caused tornado in Chicago<br> 
Your love gave me reasons to fly as well as cry,<br> 
It was no lesser than 'The Butterfly Effect' which caused changes on the go.<br> 
<em><b>Mrigank Prasoon</b></em>
			</h4>
		</div>	
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
        	<button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
